### 地點 CRUD API 測試

### 1. 登入取得認證 token
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### 2. 取得地點清單
GET http://localhost:3001/api/locations
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 3. 新增地點（使用地址）
POST http://localhost:3001/api/locations
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "測試咖啡廳",
  "description": "這是一個測試咖啡廳",
  "address": "台北市信義區信義路五段7號",
  "category": "咖啡廳",
  "rating": 4,
  "notes": "測試備註"
}

### 4. 新增地點（使用座標）
POST http://localhost:3001/api/locations
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "測試餐廳",
  "description": "這是一個測試餐廳",
  "latitude": 25.0330,
  "longitude": 121.5654,
  "category": "餐廳",
  "rating": 5,
  "notes": "座標測試"
}

### 5. 取得特定地點
GET http://localhost:3001/api/locations/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 6. 更新地點
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/locations/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "更新後的咖啡廳",
  "rating": 5,
  "notes": "更新後的備註"
}

### 7. 搜尋地點
GET http://localhost:3001/api/locations?search=咖啡
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 8. 分類篩選
GET http://localhost:3001/api/locations?category=咖啡廳
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 9. 排序
GET http://localhost:3001/api/locations?sortBy=rating&sortOrder=DESC
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 10. 取得地點統計
GET http://localhost:3001/api/locations/stats/summary
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 11. 從 Google Places 新增地點
POST http://localhost:3001/api/locations/from-google
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "placeId": "ChIJd8BlQ2BZwokRAFQEcDlJRAI",
  "category": "咖啡廳",
  "rating": 4,
  "notes": "從 Google Places 新增"
}

### 12. 刪除地點
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/locations/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 13. 測試地址自動轉座標
POST http://localhost:3001/api/locations
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "自動座標咖啡廳",
  "address": "台北101",
  "category": "咖啡廳"
}

### 14. 測試座標自動轉地址
POST http://localhost:3001/api/locations
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "自動地址餐廳",
  "latitude": 25.0330,
  "longitude": 121.5654,
  "category": "餐廳"
}

### 15. 測試更新地址重新取得座標
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/locations/2
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "台北車站"
}

### 16. 測試更新座標重新取得地址
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/locations/2
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": 25.0478,
  "longitude": 121.5170
}
